WEBVTT

00:00:58.479 --> 00:01:00.280
Lawyer Luo, the base station is fixed.

00:01:00.960 --> 00:01:03.039
It's just announcing the will.

00:01:03.039 --> 00:01:04.879
You don't necessarily have to be there.

00:01:05.359 --> 00:01:06.319
The will is with me.

00:01:06.879 --> 00:01:08.640
I must deliver the will to them personally.

00:01:08.799 --> 00:01:10.920
But the road up the mountain is still under repair.

00:01:11.200 --> 00:01:12.680
Who knows when it will be fixed.

00:01:13.560 --> 00:01:15.599
How about this, I'll contact them.

00:01:15.680 --> 00:01:17.000
And explain the situation to them.

00:01:17.959 --> 00:01:18.439
Okay.

00:01:25.480 --> 00:01:26.120
Mr. Fang.

00:01:27.400 --> 00:01:28.560
Aren't you going to say something?

00:01:29.640 --> 00:01:30.359
What am I supposed to say?

00:01:32.799 --> 00:01:33.680
The p-pendant?

00:01:34.879 --> 00:01:36.079
She says it belongs to her daughter.

00:01:36.359 --> 00:01:37.079
Well, I say it's mine.

00:01:37.079 --> 00:01:38.200
Can we even clear this up?

00:01:39.760 --> 00:01:41.599
That Ma Shan is crazy.

00:01:41.599 --> 00:01:43.560
I don't believe a word she says anyway.

00:01:44.760 --> 00:01:46.040
Her daughter is her obsession.

00:01:46.680 --> 00:01:48.079
I don't think Auntie Ma is lying.

00:01:50.040 --> 00:01:50.640
Mr. Fang.

00:01:51.200 --> 00:01:52.680
If this pendant is really yours,

00:01:53.319 --> 00:01:55.280
please explain where it came from.

00:01:56.359 --> 00:01:58.079
That is my personal item.

00:01:58.480 --> 00:02:00.840
I have the right to refuse to answer that.

00:02:02.439 --> 00:02:03.879
I think you'd better explain.

00:02:05.439 --> 00:02:07.079
Just to clear yourself of suspicion.

00:02:18.039 --> 00:02:18.879
That pendant...

00:02:20.319 --> 00:02:21.960
was given to me by Di Fu.

00:02:22.800 --> 00:02:23.759
You mean...

00:02:24.240 --> 00:02:26.639
my sister and Nana had the same pendant?

00:02:28.159 --> 00:02:29.639
They were good friends.

00:02:30.199 --> 00:02:31.919
It's not strange to have matching pendants, right?

00:02:32.599 --> 00:02:33.680
When did she give it to you?

00:02:40.919 --> 00:02:41.879
It was...

00:02:44.439 --> 00:02:47.240
after Di Fu married Mr. Zhao.

00:02:47.719 --> 00:02:49.479
This... this means...

00:02:49.479 --> 00:02:51.159
my brother was a cuckold?

00:02:51.360 --> 00:02:52.759
You adulterous couple!

00:02:53.240 --> 00:02:54.039
You piece of trash!

00:02:54.039 --> 00:02:55.280
And she left you an inheritance?

00:02:55.439 --> 00:02:55.840
I...

00:02:56.080 --> 00:02:56.879
Zhao Qihai!

00:02:57.759 --> 00:02:59.240
You insist there's something going on between us?

00:02:59.560 --> 00:02:59.960
Fine.

00:03:00.680 --> 00:03:02.039
I'll give you what you want today.

00:03:02.039 --> 00:03:02.919
We did have something going on.

00:03:03.039 --> 00:03:04.039
So what? You want to kill me?

00:03:06.080 --> 00:03:06.680
Enough, enough.

00:03:08.199 --> 00:03:09.520
Why is everyone so angry?

00:03:09.719 --> 00:03:10.240
Everyone.

00:03:12.319 --> 00:03:13.199
How is Auntie Ma doing?

00:03:13.400 --> 00:03:15.080
She just took her medicine and fell asleep.

00:03:15.960 --> 00:03:17.159
Breakfast is ready.

00:03:17.159 --> 00:03:19.080
Would you like to eat something first?

00:03:19.400 --> 00:03:20.000
Breakfast is ready.

00:03:20.319 --> 00:03:20.759
Uh...

00:03:21.400 --> 00:03:21.719
let's have breakfast.

00:03:21.719 --> 00:03:21.960
Please.

00:03:22.280 --> 00:03:23.319
Have some breakfast and cool down.

00:03:25.280 --> 00:03:26.080
Such a temper.

00:03:53.039 --> 00:03:53.719
I checked.

00:03:54.080 --> 00:03:55.000
I didn't find anything.

00:03:56.680 --> 00:03:58.319
Fang Qiu said his door wasn't locked yesterday.

00:03:58.639 --> 00:03:59.879
Anyone could have entered.

00:04:02.439 --> 00:04:04.680
If that's really the case,

00:04:06.000 --> 00:04:07.879
someone waited until he was asleep,

00:04:08.360 --> 00:04:09.840
took the pendant off his neck.

00:04:10.639 --> 00:04:12.159
Why didn't he react at all?

00:04:13.199 --> 00:04:16.360
His explanation is that he was drunk.

00:04:18.319 --> 00:04:19.680
If that's really true,

00:04:20.800 --> 00:04:22.240
this person must know

00:04:22.240 --> 00:04:23.720
that the pendant is connected to Nana.

00:04:24.920 --> 00:04:25.959
That's why they put the pendant

00:04:25.959 --> 00:04:27.439
by Auntie Ma Shan's pillow.

00:04:27.920 --> 00:04:28.680
That's not all.

00:04:31.560 --> 00:04:33.319
The ring. Why do you have it?

00:04:34.959 --> 00:04:36.360
I found it at my door last night.

00:04:37.000 --> 00:04:38.319
I think the person who left this ring

00:04:38.720 --> 00:04:41.279
and the one who took Fang Qiu's necklace are the same person.

00:04:42.600 --> 00:04:44.680
Who would know about these things?

00:04:48.120 --> 00:04:49.480
Could it really be your sister?

00:04:56.040 --> 00:04:56.519
Don't mind me.

00:04:57.480 --> 00:04:58.279
I just said it without thinking.

00:05:00.160 --> 00:05:00.920
Inspector Qi.

00:05:01.639 --> 00:05:02.160
Miss Li.

00:05:02.920 --> 00:05:04.920
Auntie Ma Shan is missing again.

00:05:05.879 --> 00:05:06.680
Let's split up and look for her.

00:05:08.040 --> 00:05:08.680
Meet back at the dining room.

00:05:09.439 --> 00:05:10.160
Auntie Ma!

00:05:11.000 --> 00:05:11.720
Auntie Ma!

00:05:31.920 --> 00:05:33.120
Still no news from Lawyer Luo?

00:05:42.879 --> 00:05:43.759
Ah Qiu.

00:05:45.079 --> 00:05:47.560
Did you kill Ma Shan?

00:05:48.759 --> 00:05:50.279
I've been questioned by you all this time.

00:05:50.519 --> 00:05:52.240
I wouldn't have time even if I wanted to kill her.

00:06:11.959 --> 00:06:12.759
Auntie Ma

00:06:13.680 --> 00:06:14.319
What's wrong?

00:06:14.639 --> 00:06:15.040
Did I scare you?

00:06:15.040 --> 00:06:15.680
How did you end up here?

00:06:16.319 --> 00:06:18.040
I saw a man.

00:06:19.519 --> 00:06:21.360
A man whose face I couldn't see clearly.

00:06:21.680 --> 00:06:22.079
Let's go.

00:06:24.720 --> 00:06:26.560
Auntie Ma, how did you end up here?

00:06:26.560 --> 00:06:27.680
I don't remember either.

00:06:28.240 --> 00:06:29.199
I woke up and I was here.

00:06:31.040 --> 00:06:33.439
It must be Zhao Qishan's ghost that brought me here.

00:06:37.680 --> 00:06:38.279
It's a ghost.

00:06:39.079 --> 00:06:40.040
It's Zhao Qishan's ghost.

00:06:40.720 --> 00:06:41.519
It was him.

00:06:42.279 --> 00:06:43.360
There are no ghosts.

00:06:43.360 --> 00:06:44.360
You're seeing things.

00:06:45.240 --> 00:06:47.600
Miss Li, where did you find Auntie Ma Shan?

00:06:48.480 --> 00:06:50.160
I found her in the study.

00:06:50.639 --> 00:06:51.000
No.

00:06:51.480 --> 00:06:53.439
Why were you looking for her?

00:06:53.800 --> 00:06:54.160
I was...

00:06:54.399 --> 00:06:55.600
I really, really...

00:06:55.600 --> 00:06:57.160
I can't take it anymore.

00:06:58.360 --> 00:06:59.160
Miss Li.

00:07:01.199 --> 00:07:01.959
By now...

00:07:03.079 --> 00:07:04.759
We still haven't heard your story.

00:07:05.920 --> 00:07:08.720
I don't know where to start.

00:07:10.079 --> 00:07:10.759
After all...

00:07:11.839 --> 00:07:13.759
I haven't seen my sister in a long time.

00:07:15.040 --> 00:07:16.879
Memories from childhood are very blurry.

00:07:18.079 --> 00:07:19.879
Trying to brush us off again?

00:07:20.839 --> 00:07:21.720
Of course not.

00:07:23.079 --> 00:07:24.279
Since I promised...

00:07:26.439 --> 00:07:27.360
I will definitely tell it.

00:07:31.560 --> 00:07:33.079
The earliest home in my memory...

00:07:35.720 --> 00:07:37.079
...had no color.

00:07:40.639 --> 00:07:41.519
Xiao Ran, come here.

00:07:42.079 --> 00:07:43.279
Look what I found.

00:07:47.920 --> 00:07:48.519
Money.

00:07:48.839 --> 00:07:50.199
Finally, I can buy a new pair of shoes.

00:07:50.480 --> 00:07:51.920
And I can take you to eat a bowl of boat noodles.

00:07:52.879 --> 00:07:55.120
Boat noodles! I want boat noodles!

00:07:59.480 --> 00:08:00.839
I'll take you to eat right now.

00:08:00.959 --> 00:08:02.879
But Xiao Ran, you must not tell Mom and Dad.

00:08:02.879 --> 00:08:03.839
That we found money.

00:08:04.079 --> 00:08:04.600
Understand?

00:08:05.399 --> 00:08:06.120
You must not say a word.

00:08:08.639 --> 00:08:09.839
You hopeless gambler.

00:08:10.120 --> 00:08:11.079
You stole my money.

00:08:11.439 --> 00:08:12.560
This is my hard-earned money.

00:08:12.560 --> 00:08:13.680
I didn't! I'm not done with you!

00:08:13.920 --> 00:08:14.480
Sis.

00:08:15.240 --> 00:08:17.319
Let's just tell Mom and Dad.

00:08:17.720 --> 00:08:18.399
Otherwise...

00:08:18.879 --> 00:08:20.319
They'll keep fighting.

00:08:20.319 --> 00:08:21.120
This is my money.

00:08:21.920 --> 00:08:22.399
No.

00:08:22.680 --> 00:08:23.680
We absolutely can't tell.

00:08:24.399 --> 00:08:25.519
I'm leaving tomorrow.

00:08:26.079 --> 00:08:27.480
Leaving? Where are you going?

00:08:28.519 --> 00:08:29.759
You dare go find another man?

00:08:30.040 --> 00:08:31.040
So what if I did?

00:08:31.439 --> 00:08:32.919
There are plenty of men out there waiting for me.

00:08:34.840 --> 00:08:36.080
Mom.

00:08:37.120 --> 00:08:38.519
Mom.

00:08:40.840 --> 00:08:42.039
Mom.

00:08:42.039 --> 00:08:43.679
Don't leave us behind.

00:08:44.519 --> 00:08:45.080
Xiao Ran.

00:08:45.440 --> 00:08:46.399
Listen to Mom.

00:08:46.399 --> 00:08:48.000
Mom will be back very soon.

00:08:48.000 --> 00:08:49.919
Then I'll buy you lots and lots of new clothes.

00:08:49.919 --> 00:08:51.360
And lots and lots of toys.

00:08:51.360 --> 00:08:53.480
And take you to eat delicious food, okay?

00:08:55.480 --> 00:08:56.960
Don't cry. Listen to Mom.

00:08:58.639 --> 00:08:59.679
Really?

00:09:03.279 --> 00:09:05.279
Really. Trust Mom.

00:09:07.000 --> 00:09:08.600
Xiao Ran, take good care of your sister.

00:09:13.840 --> 00:09:17.120
Mom, I beg you.

00:09:17.120 --> 00:09:19.399
Don't leave us behind.

00:09:22.000 --> 00:09:22.679
Don't go.

00:09:22.679 --> 00:09:23.320
From that day on...

00:09:23.320 --> 00:09:24.519
Mom...

00:09:24.720 --> 00:09:26.320
I never saw my mom again.

00:09:27.799 --> 00:09:28.799
Later I learned...

00:09:29.919 --> 00:09:31.480
What a lie really is.

00:09:31.639 --> 00:09:34.480
Children without a mom are pitiful.

00:09:35.759 --> 00:09:37.080
My dad was a hopeless gambler by nature.

00:09:38.279 --> 00:09:40.399
He didn't care if my sister and I lived or died.

00:09:42.200 --> 00:09:42.559
Boss.

00:09:42.759 --> 00:09:43.679
Without my sister...

00:09:45.519 --> 00:09:46.840
I probably would have died long ago.

00:09:48.919 --> 00:09:49.840
Vegetarian or meat?

00:09:50.720 --> 00:09:51.200
Meat.

00:09:51.840 --> 00:09:52.279
Here.

00:10:00.399 --> 00:10:01.840
You two, stand still!

00:10:03.000 --> 00:10:03.879
You stole something!

00:10:19.320 --> 00:10:21.120
Little friend, is this your home?